<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbfcf06f7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s14331"><num value="14331">§ 14331.</num><heading> Purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purpose of this subchapter is to phase out the use of batteries containing mercury.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbfcf06f8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/142/tII/s202">Pub. L. 104–142, title II, § 202</ref>, <date date="1996-05-13">May 13, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1336">110 Stat. 1336</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
